Interface MinPriorityQueue<E,​P extends java.lang.Comparable<P>>

Type Parameters:

All Known Implementing Classes:
MinHeap
public interface MinPriorityQueue<E,​P extends java.lang.Comparable<P>>
extends java.lang.Iterable<PQEntry<E,​P>>
A "min priority queue". The item with the highest priority is the one with the minimum value according to the Comparable interface.
